# Pull Requests Checklist

Assignee:

- \[ \] code commented?
- \[ \] tests added / passed?
- \[ \] are tests covering all cases?
- \[ \] documentation added / updated?
- \[ \] pre-commit checks passed?
- \[ \] pipelines passed?

Reviewer:

- \[ \] are there any code smells?
- \[ \] did pipeline pass?
- \[ \] is the code well documented?
- \[ \] are the tests passing and covering all cases?
